     Where can I buy iÖGO Frozen Yogurt?         iÖGO Frozen Yogurt is available in all major retail stores across Canada.

To explore both online and in-store options, select the Products tab in the top banner and click the "Where to Buy" button below the flavour of iÖGO Frozen Yogurt you want! A pop-up will provide options for shopping online or locating nearby stores by entering a postal code or city.
     Where are iÖGO Frozen Yogurt made?         iÖGO Frozen Yogurt is made at the Nestlé Ice Cream factory in London, ON.
     What is the source of dairy in iÖGO Frozen Yogurt?         All our dairy ingredients are from Canada. 
     Does iÖGO contain any artificial colours or flavours?         All IÖGO Frozen Yogurt products do not contain any artificial colors or flavours.
     What is the shelf life of iÖGO Frozen Yogurt          The recommended shelf life of IÖGO Frozen Yogurt products are 1 year.
     Is iÖGO Frozen Yogurt Kosher?         All iÖGO products are certified Kosher (COR).
